name: Hellowicked 02: Wreck Havoc
description:
"When the slugs penetrate you feel a burning sensation/ Getting closer to God in a tight situation/ Now, take these words home and think it through/ Or the next rhyme I write might be about you" - Shook Ones, Part II

"The sinister minister. Havoc is the obvious next choice for our wicked All Hallow's series. As one half of The Infamous NY crew that brought darkness into hip hop with their signature hardcore lyricism and grim production, the man is the centerpiece of a sound that turned grisly beats and gruesome tales into an East Coast renaissance." - Krowbar
